⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
At the Dell Extreme Computing Test Lab, Dell Rugged notebooks and tablets are tested to withstand the world’s harshest environments. 🔥💧🔩

Watch how devices are examined and evaluated with a wide variety of military-grade measures that include extreme heat/cold, water ingress-protection, salt-fog, drop, vibration and more.
